2.Created custom components in Plant 3D using Python scripts (Cable Tray):

I created a custom parametric component using Plant 3D Python scripting

The component was a Cable Tray with configurable dimensions

I defined parameters like length, width, height, thickness

I generated geometry using Plant 3D primitive functions

I registered the script so it appears in Spec Editor and model palette.


