3.Text Manager-Revit:

User clicks Text Manager button in Revit

Plugin reads text notes and text types using Revit API

Plugin filters data based on text size, type, or view

Plugin performs the selected action (highlight, replace, view, purge)

Changes are committed using a Transaction.


------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4.Level and Grid Size:

User clicks the Levels & Grids Manager button

Plugin collects Levels and Grids using Revit API

Plugin reads their annotation properties (text size & symbol size)

User selects new circle size and text size

Plugin updates elements inside a Transaction


